i-tourists-in-gaza-our-curiosity-turned-into-blindness/0000018f-b49e-dfc6-a3ef-b5de42d90000</guid></item><item><title>战后巴勒斯坦权力机构还会继续管理加沙吗？</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-27/ty-article/.premium/will-the-palestinian-authority-even-be-around-to-govern-gaza-after-the-war/0000018f-ba01-dca9-a5cf-be0133580000</link><description>财政部长贝扎莱尔·斯莫特里奇和以色列极右翼决心在巴勒斯坦权力机构有机会从哈马斯手中接管飞地之前让其破产</description><pubDate>Mon, 27 May 2024 12:35:07 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-27/ty-article/.premium/will-the-palestinian-authority-even-be-around-to-govern-gaza-after-the-war/0000018f-ba01-dca9-a5cf-be0133580000</guid></item><item><title>将以色列踢出国际足联可能有助于结束加沙战争</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2024-05-27/ty-article-opinion/.premium/kicking-israel-out-of-fifa-could-help-end-the-gaza-war/0000018f-b9aa-dcd7-abff-bdabda3c0000</link><description>我们看到国际压力对以色列政府的影响有限，但在内塔尼亚胡支持者过多的足球阵营中，文化制裁的力量可能会产生前所未有的影响</description><pubDate>Mon, 27 May 2024 11:54:12 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2024-05-27/ty-article-opinion/.premium/kicking-israel-out-of-fifa-could-help-end-the-gaza-war/0000018f-b9aa-dcd7-abff-bdabda3c0000</guid></item><item><title>“节日快乐”：右翼以色列记者庆祝拉法袭击，将其比作 Lag Ba&amp;#39;Omer 篝火</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-27/ty-article/.premium/right-wing-israeli-journalists-celebrate-rafah-attack-likening-it-to-lag-baomer-bonfire/0000018f-b983-dca9-a5cf-bd832e6e0000</link><description>据巴勒斯坦卫生工作者称，以色列记者伊农·马加尔(Yinon Magal)在谈到以色列对加沙南部拉法的袭击时表示，“今年拉法的中心篝火造成至少35人死亡”</description><pubDate>Mon, 27 May 2024 11:06:18 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-27/ty-article/.premium/right-wing-israeli-journalists-celebrate-rafah-attack-likening-it-to-lag-baomer-bonfire/0000018f-b983-dca9-a5cf-bd832e6e0000</guid></item><item><title>本-格维尔违反高等法院命令，绕过警察局长下令停职警察</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-27/ty-article/.premium/violating-high-court-order-ben-gvir-bypasses-police-chief-to-order-suspension-of-cops/0000018f-b929-d24f-a5df-ffef236f0000</link><description>尽管警察局长已经亲自下令停职，但本格维尔绕过他的权力，直接去找边防警察局长。在他与部长之间日益紧张的情况下，最高警察将这个问题提交给司法部长，这是前所未有的举动</description><pubDate>Mon, 27 May 2024 10:49:31 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-27/ty-article/.premium/violating-high-court-order-ben-gvir-bypasses-police-chief-to-order-suspension-of-cops/0000018f-b929-d24f-a5df-ffef236f0000</guid></item><item><title>世界谴责以色列对拉法的“可怕的、不公正的”袭击；要求国际法院作出裁决</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-27/ty-article/eu-israel-continues-military-action-despite-icj-order-u-s-looks-into-rafah-attack/0000018f-b89e-df13-a3af-bc9ef6450000</link><description>巴勒斯坦人报告称，加沙流离失所者的帐篷遭到袭击，造成 45 人死亡；以色列军队声称这次袭击针对的是哈马斯官员，并正在调查“无关个人”遭到袭击的报道；欧盟最高外交官要求以色列执行国际法院对拉法的裁决</description><pubDate>Mon, 27 May 2024 06:42:29 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-27/ty-article/eu-israel-continues-military-action-despite-icj-order-u-s-looks-into-rafah-attack/0000018f-b89e-df13-a3af-bc9ef6450000</guid></item><item><title>以色列称拉法平民可能死于袭击哈马斯官员引发的火灾；死亡人数达45人</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-27/ty-article-live/palestinians-report-at-least-35-killed-by-israeli-strikes-on-displaced-area-in-rafah/0000018f-b80a-d24f-a5df-feee2ae40007</link><description>以色列国防军首席律师：拉法事件“非常严重”；以色列国防军警方发起约 70 项调查，包括针对斯德泰曼监狱设施的调查 ■ 白宫关于拉法袭击：了解报道，收集更多信息 ■ 巴勒斯坦权力机构：以色列对拉法的袭击“跨越所有边界”，呼吁国际社会立即干预 ■ 以色列国防军宣布两名士兵死亡 ■ 战时内阁召开会议讨论人质交易</description><pubDate>Mon, 27 May 2024 03:42:59 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-27/ty-article-live/palestinians-report-at-least-35-killed-by-israeli-strikes-on-displaced-area-in-rafah/0000018f-b80a-d24f-a5df-feee2ae40007</guid></item><item><title>国防部长加兰特批评甘茨支持正统军队豁免法</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-27/ty-article/.premium/defense-minister-gallant-criticizes-gantz-for-support-of-haredi-army-exemption-law/0000018f-b720-d7ed-a7ef-bf3e10e70000</link><description>加兰特说，正统派政党的代表告诉他，内阁成员本尼·甘茨表示，他支持该法案的条件是他们同意提前选举。甘茨否认所有说法，称正统党派退出谈判</description><pubDate>Mon, 27 May 2024 03:12:58 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-27/ty-article/.premium/defense-minister-gallant-criticizes-gantz-for-support-of-haredi-army-exemption-law/0000018f-b720-d7ed-a7ef-bf3e10e70000</guid></item><item><title>以色列警察与犹太信徒在梅龙山庆祝活动中发生冲突</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-26/ty-article/.premium/israel-police-jewish-worshippers-clash-at-mt-meron-celebration/0000018f-b61e-d7ed-a7ef-bf3e1c4e0000</link><description>尽管由于真主党的袭击，该地点已被宣布为军事禁区，但仍有数千人参加 Lag Ba&amp;#39;Omer 庆祝活动；视频显示一名警察将一名老人推倒在地</description><pubDate>Sun, 26 May 2024 18:38:36 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-26/ty-article/.premium/israel-police-jewish-worshippers-clash-at-mt-meron-celebration/0000018f-b61e-d7ed-a7ef-bf3e1c4e0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列国防军人质负责人：我们绝望了，不会与这个政府达成协议</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-26/ty-article/idf-hostage-chief-we-are-desperate-there-will-be-no-deal-with-this-government/0000018f-b609-d24f-a5df-feef59780000</link><description>据第 12 频道报道，这位负责人表示，“我推动的协议将包括归还所有人质，而哈马斯则坚称这将包括结束战争”。内塔尼亚胡：“谈判团队内部的冲突只会加强哈马斯的地位”</description><pubDate>Sun, 26 May 2024 18:36:10 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-26/ty-article/idf-hostage-chief-we-are-desperate-there-will-be-no-deal-with-this-government/0000018f-b609-d24f-a5df-feef59780000</guid></item><item><title>内塔尼亚胡的忠诚者在以色列内战的道路上创造了另一个里程碑</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/haaretz-today/2024-05-26/ty-article/.highlight/netanyahus-loyalists-spawn-another-milestone-on-the-path-to-civil-war-in-israel/0000018f-b5ef-dca9-a5cf-b5ef4f370000</link><description>是否有任何预备役人员组织等待内塔尼亚胡的命令，即使下达撤退命令，仍继续在加沙作战？几乎可以肯定不是，即使有，这个视频也不能证明这一点。但让以色列人担心情况可能会是这样，这对内塔尼亚胡和极右翼来说是有利的</description><pubDate>Sun, 26 May 2024 18:15:59 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/haaretz-today/2024-05-26/ty-article/.highlight/netanyahus-loyalists-spawn-another-milestone-on-the-path-to-civil-war-in-israel/0000018f-b5ef-dca9-a5cf-b5ef4f370000</guid></item><item><title>数千人参加哈南·亚布隆卡的葬礼队伍，其尸体从加沙被打捞上来</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-26/ty-article/.premium/thousands-join-funeral-procession-for-hostage-whose-body-was-retrieved-from-gaza/0000018f-b5de-d24f-a5df-fffef00b0000</link><description>家人将这次葬礼定为人质家属的希望游行，许多参与者都系着黄丝带前来。亚布隆卡的母亲赞叹道：“这不是我想要的结局，但至少你回到了我们身边。”</description><pubDate>Sun, 26 May 2024 18:03:58 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-26/ty-article/.premium/thousands-join-funeral-procession-for-hostage-whose-body-was-retrieved-from-gaza/0000018f-b5de-d24f-a5df-fffef00b0000</guid></item><item><title>研究表明，喝咖啡因的蚂蚁可能会产生更好的蚂蚁陷阱</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/science-and-health/2024-05-26/ty-article/ants-on-caffeine-could-lead-to-a-better-ant-trap-study-suggests/0000018f-b578-dca9-a5cf-b57893940000</link><description>这正是我们一直想要的：具有卓越学习能力的嗡嗡作响的觅食蚂蚁。但一项新的研究表明，这可能会导致更好的、含有咖啡因的蚂蚁陷阱</description><pubDate>Sun, 26 May 2024 17:31:57 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/science-and-health/2024-05-26/ty-article/ants-on-caffeine-could-lead-to-a-better-ant-trap-study-suggests/0000018f-b578-dca9-a5cf-b57893940000</guid></item><item><title>以色列战争第 233 天：以色列国防军终止呼吁叛变的男子的预备役服役</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/2024-05-26/ty-article/.premium/israel-at-war-day-233-idf-terminates-reserve-service-of-man-who-called-for-mutiny/0000018f-b5ca-d33c-a5bf-ffdb20d70001</link><description>哈马斯自 1 月以来首次对以色列中部发动攻击 ■ 据 CNN 报道，释放人质/停火协议谈判将于周二恢复 ■ 战时内阁部长甘茨提出建议，成立一个调查委员会，调查 10 月 7 日和加沙战争 ■ 大约 200 辆援助卡车通过与以色列接壤的凯雷姆沙洛姆过境点进入加沙 ■ 战争进入 233 天后，您需要了解以下内容</description><pubDate>Sun, 26 May 2024 16:59:57 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/2024-05-26/ty-article/.premium/israel-at-war-day-233-idf-terminates-reserve-service-of-man-who-called-for-mutiny/0000018f-b5ca-d33c-a5bf-ffdb20d70001</guid></item><item><title>“丑闻”：西班牙外长就“哈马斯感谢西班牙”视频回击以色列外长卡茨</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-26/ty-article/outrageous-spanish-fm-lashes-out-at-israeli-counterpart-katz-over-gracias-hamas-video/0000018f-b5b7-d33c-a5bf-ffb75e560000</link><description>在西班牙宣布承认巴勒斯坦国后，以色列外交部长以色列卡茨在 X 上发布了一段短视频，称“哈马斯：西班牙之恩”</description><pubDate>Sun, 26 May 2024 16:50:27 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-26/ty-article/outrageous-spanish-fm-lashes-out-at-israeli-counterpart-katz-over-gracias-hamas-video/0000018f-b5b7-d33c-a5bf-ffb75e560000</guid></item><item><title>犹太纽约人纠结是否参加今年的以色列日游行</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2024-05-26/ty-article/.premium/jewish-new-yorkers-wrestle-with-whether-to-march-in-this-years-israel-day-parade/0000018f-b491-dfc6-a3ef-b5ddd2540000</link><description>被扣押在加沙的人质代表定于 6 月 2 日游行，但广受诟病的内塔尼亚胡政府的四名成员也将游行 — — 让许多外籍以色列人和自由派犹太人陷入困境</description><pubDate>Sun, 26 May 2024 16:43:53 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2024-05-26/ty-article/.premium/jewish-new-yorkers-wrestle-with-whether-to-march-in-this-years-israel-day-parade/0000018f-b491-dfc6-a3ef-b5ddd2540000</guid></item><item><title>以色列国防军公布了两名在加沙战斗中丧生的士兵的名字</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-26/ty-article/israeli-soldier-dies-of-wounds-sustained-in-gaza-combat-last-week/0000018f-b59a-d08f-adcf-b7fa97b80000</link><description>中士。 20 岁的贝扎莱尔·兹维·科瓦奇 (Betzalel Zvi Kovach) 上周三在加沙北部受伤，并于周日因伤死亡。中士。 20 岁的 Sahar Sudaei 周日在加沙北部被杀</description><pubDate>Sun, 26 May 2024 16:15:00 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-26/ty-article/israeli-soldier-dies-of-wounds-sustained-in-gaza-combat-last-week/0000018f-b59a-d08f-adcf-b7fa97b80000</guid></item><item><title>舒默参议员，不要邀请内塔尼亚胡。他不是你的盟友或朋友。他从来都不是</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2024-05-26/ty-article/.premium/senator-schumer-dont-invite-netanyahu-hes-not-your-ally-or-your-friend-he-never-was/0000018f-b452-d390-ab8f-f5da4a7b0000</link><description>向以色列坚定的民主党盟友传达的信息：不要邀请本杰明·内塔尼亚胡参加国会。他的唯一目的是在执行特朗普的命令时破坏美国总统乔·拜登的连任竞选</description><pubDate>Sun, 26 May 2024 15:41:55 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2024-05-26/ty-article/.premium/senator-schumer-dont-invite-netanyahu-hes-not-your-ally-or-your-friend-he-never-was/0000018f-b452-d390-ab8f-f5da4a7b0000</guid></item></channel></rss>